OL,3,CInquest hears 15-year-old died from
OL,4,Cdrowning
OL,6,FAn inquest into the death of a 15-year-
OL,7,Fold boy in Lincoln last month has
OL,8,Fheard that he died from drowning.
OL,10,FDeclan Sawyer died at Swanholme Lakes
OL,11,Fduring a period of hot weather in late
OL,12,FMay, which saw a number of similar
OL,13,Fincidents around the country.
OL,15,FHaving been called to the lake at
OL,16,Faround 2.30pm on Sunday 24 May,
OL,17,FLincolnshire Police confirmed at
OL,18,F10.25pm on Sunday 25 May that his body
OL,19,Fhad been recovered.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
