PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782731897
OL,3,CInquest hears 15-year-old died from
OL,4,Cdrowning
OL,6,FThe inquest at the Myle Cross Centre
OL,7,Fin Lincoln heard confirmation that the
OL,8,Fcause of death was drowning and
OL,9,Fadjourned the inquest to a provisional
OL,10,Fdate of 23 November.
OL,12,FIn an earlier tribute to Declan, his
OL,13,Ffather Carl described him as "a funny
OL,14,Fand outgoing young man who loved
OL,15,Ffishing and football".
OL,17,FHe said: "He had a very cheeky smile
OL,18,Fand the personality to match. He was
OL,19,Fvery much loved by his friends and
OL,20,Ffamily, and will be missed dearly by
OL,21,Fmany."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,339,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782731897
OL,3,CInquest hears 15-year-old died from
OL,4,Cdrowning
OL,6,FHoping to raise awareness of the
OL,7,Fdangers of open water, his family said
OL,8,Fthey would like to raise awareness of
OL,9,Fthe dangers of open water.
OL,11,FHis father Carl said: "Please can all
OL,12,Fparents, friends and family make their
OL,13,Fchildren aware of the dangers
OL,14,Fsurrounding water."
OL,16,FThe Priory Lincoln Academy school also
OL,17,Fpaid tribute, saying that the "entire
OL,18,FPriory Lincoln learning community is
OL,19,Fgrieving alongside Declan's family and
OL,20,Ffriends".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
