OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F338A1782731897
OL,3,CInquest hears 15-year-old died from
OL,4,Cdrowning
OL,6,FAmid a further heatwave in mid-June, a
OL,7,Fred heat health alert has been
OL,8,Fextended in parts of the country
OL,9,Fincluding Lincolnshire.
OL,11,FDuring the peak of the current
OL,12,Fheatwave, the temperature could come
OL,13,Fclose to the UK's all-time high of
OL,14,F40.3C, which was measured in Coningsby
OL,15,Fin Lincolnshire in July 2022.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
